'''芬恩·伍法德'''（{{lang-en|Finn Wolfhard}}，{{bd|2002年|12月23日|catidx=Wolfhard}}）<ref name=gamegrumps>{{cite episode |title=Crash Tag Team Racing with Special Guest Finn Wolfhard |station=[[Game_Grumps|Game Grumps]] |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H-m10elC8po |series=Guest Grumps |air-date=2017-01-14 |minutes=10:47 |access-date=2018-01-07 |archive-date=2017-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610065555/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H-m10elC8po&app=desktop |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一位[[加拿大|加拿大]][[男演員|男演員]]、[[音樂家|音樂家]]。他最出名的是演出是[[Netflix|Netflix]]的科幻恐怖影集《[[怪奇物語|怪奇物語]]》（2016年）中的麥克·威勒。他的電影角色包括在[[史蒂芬·金|史蒂芬·金]]（Stephen King）的恐怖小說《[[牠_(電影)|牠]]》 （2017年）及其續集《[[牠：第二章|牠：第二章]]》（2019年）的{{link-en|瑞奇·托茲|Richie Tozier}}、在劇情片《[[金翅雀_(電影)|金翅雀 (電影)]]》（2019年）中的鮑里斯·帕夫利科夫斯基（Boris Pavlikovsky）、《[[阿達一族_(2019年電影)|阿達一族 (2019年電影)]]》(2019年)的{{link-en|帕斯利·亞當斯|Pugsley Addams}}配音。在超自然電影《[[魔鬼剋星_未來世|魔鬼剋星 未來世]]》（2021年）的特雷弗。伍法德憑藉喜劇短片《{{link-en|Night Shifts|Night Shifts (film)}}》(2020年)完成了他的導演處女作。

他曾為加拿大的龐克搖滾樂團Pup的MV "Guilt Trip"中演出，飾演年輕時的Stefan Babcock。他是搖滾樂隊[[Calpurnia樂團|Calpurnia樂團]]的主唱和吉他手，目前是[[The_Aubreys樂團|The Aubreys樂團]]的成員。
==早期生活==
伍法德出生於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[不列顛哥倫比亞省|不列顛哥倫比亞省]]的[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]，擁有[[德國人|德國]]、[[法國人|法國]]及[[猶太|猶太]]血統。<ref name=vulture>{{cite web |url=http://www.vulture.com/2016/07/stranger-things-finn-wolfhard-on-kissing-scenes.html |title=''Stranger Things'' ' Finn Wolfhard on Kissing Scenes and How He Became an Actor |website={{le|Vulture.com|Vulture.com}} |first=Jen |last=Chaney |date=2016-07-25 |accessdate=2017-02-01 |archive-date=2016-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918094507/http://www.vulture.com/2016/07/stranger-things-finn-wolfhard-on-kissing-scenes.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他有一個同為演員的哥哥尼克。當他沒在拍攝電影時，他則在[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]的天主教學校就讀。
==職業生涯==

===表演===
伍法德從克雷格列表[[克雷格列表|克雷格列表]]獲得了他的第一份表演工作。<ref name="dazed33767">{{cite web |url=http://www.dazeddigital.com/artsandculture/article/33767/1/finn-wolfhard-stranger-things |title=Finn Wolfhard: sci-fi 'it-boy' |work=[[Dazed|Dazed]] |first=Colleen |last=Nika |date=November 22, 2016}}</ref>他在《[[地球百子|地球百子]]》中以Zoran的身份首次亮相，隨後在《[[超自然檔案|超自然檔案]]》中扮演Jordie Pinsky的角色。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2016/07/25/vancouvers-finn-wolfhard-loving-the-80s-in-stranger-things.html |title=Vancouver's Finn Wolfhard loving the '80s in Stranger Things |website=[[Toronto_Star|Toronto Star]] |first=Victoria |last=Ahearn |date=July 25, 2016 |access-date=February 8, 2017}}</ref>

2016年，伍法德開始在[[Netflix|Netflix]]系列《[[怪奇物語|怪奇物語]]》中扮演麥克·威勒。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2015/08/duffer-bros-netflix-series-stranger-things-young-cast-1201502552 |title=Duffer Bros. Netflix Supernatural Drama Series Sets Young Cast, Gets Title |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=August 20, 2015 |access-date=February 8, 2017}}</ref>在看到一個公開的選角後，他通過影片試鏡了這個角色。<ref name="dazed33767"/>伍法德和劇裡其他演員一起獲得了戲劇系列劇組的傑出表演獎。<ref name="sag-awards">{{cite web |url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/12/14/2017-sag-awards-nominations |title=SAG Awards nominations 2017: See the full list |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |first=Joely |last=Nolfi |date=December 14, 2016}}</ref>

他還在[[Netflix|Netflix]]動畫系列《{{link-en|新神偷卡門|Carmen Sandiego (TV series)}}》中飾演“玩家”，是主角的主要幫兇和朋友。該系列於2019年1月18日首播。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/netflix-reboots-carmen-sandiego-gina-rodriguez-995072 |title=Netflix Reboots 'Carmen Sandiego' With Gina Rodriguez |date=April 18, 2017 |first=Jackie |last=Strause |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=April 18, 2017}}</ref>

伍法德在[[史蒂芬·金|史蒂芬·金]]的電影《[[牠|牠]]》中飾演{{link-en|瑞奇·托茲|Richie Tozier}}的故事處女作，該片於 2017 年 9 月 8 日上映<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/stephen-kings-it-release-date-set-by-warner-bros |title=Stephen King's 'It' Release Date Set by Warner Bros |website=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |first=Thom |last=Geier |date=April 22, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/news/film/stranger-things-star-to-appear-in-remake-of-steph-874057 |title='Stranger Things' star to appear in remake of Stephen King's 'It' |work=[[NME|NME]] |first=Luke |last=Morgan Britton |date=August 20, 2016 |access-date=February 8, 2017}}</ref> 。有趣的巧合是《[[怪奇物語|怪奇物語]]》和《[[牠|牠]]》中的演員設定都是在80年代的背景。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/it-movie/news/a837370/it-director-andy-muschietti-refused-watch-stranger-things-until-his-film-finished/ |title=Exclusive: IT director Andy Muschietti says Stranger Things' Finn Wolfhard casting was a complete coincidence |date=September 6, 2017 |first=Jamie |last=Graham |work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |access-date=November 27, 2017}}</ref>根據伍法德的說法，最初[[凱瑞·福永|凱瑞·福永]]是編劇時找他演{{link-en|瑞奇·托茲|Richie Tozier}}，但當[[凱瑞·福永|凱瑞·福永]]因創作差異而離開項目時，這個角色落空後，這讓他去追求飾演《[[怪奇物語|怪奇物語]]》。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/herocomplex/la-et-hc-horror-finn-wolfhard-stranger-things-20171013-htmlstory.html|title=Finn Wolfhard shares his texts from the 'It' and 'Stranger Things' gang |date=October 13, 2017 |first=Meredith |last=Woerner |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |access-date=November 27, 2017}}</ref>[[安迪·馬希提|安迪·馬希提]]與《[[牠|牠]]》結緣，伍法德就不得不重新試鏡{{link-en|瑞奇·托茲|Richie Tozier}}的角色。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/08/02/stranger-things-creators-on-how-season-1-ended-and-where-season-2-will-go?page=3 |title=Stranger Things Creators on How Season 1 Ended and Where Season 2 Will Go |date=August 2, 2016 |first=Eric |last=Goldman |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |access-date=November 27, 2017}}</ref>

2017年10月20日，伍法德與他的前經紀公司{{link-en|APA|Agency for the Performing Arts}}分道揚鑣，並解雇了前經紀人Tyler Grasham，此前有人指控Tyler Grasham對有抱負的年輕男演員進行性侵犯。<ref name="Gardener">{{Cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/stranger-things-star-finn-wolfhard-fires-agent-sexual-abuse-claim-1049897 |title='Stranger Things' Star Finn Wolfhard Fires Agent Over Former Actor's Sexual Abuse Claim |date=October 20, 2017 |first=Chris |last=Gardener |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=June 1, 2019}}</ref>伍法德本人沒有受到攻擊。<ref name="Gardener"/>2018年1月9日，伍法德與[[創新藝人經紀公司|創新藝人經紀公司]]（{{link-en|CAA|Creative Artists Agency}}）簽約。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/finn-wolfhard-signs-caa-1073114 |title='Stranger Things' Star Finn Wolfhard Signs With CAA (Exclusive) |date=January 9, 2018 |first=Rebecca |last=Sun |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=June 1, 2019}}</ref>

2018年，伍法德在[[肯·馬里諾|肯·馬里諾]]導演的音樂喜劇電影{{link-en|《與狗狗一起生活》|Dog Days (2018 film)}}中扮演了一個無私且體貼的披薩送貨員Tyler。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2017/09/it-movie-stranger-things-finn-wolfhard-dog-days-1202175139/ |title='It' & 'Stranger Things' Star Finn Wolfhard Cast In 'Dog Days' |date=September 22, 2017 |first=Amanda |last=N'Duka |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=November 27, 2017}}</ref>

2019年，伍法德在《[[牠：第二章|牠：第二章]]》(2019)中重新扮演年輕的{{link-en|瑞奇·托茲|Richie Tozier}}的角色。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/it-chapter-2-trailer-stephen-king-1203207671/ |title='It: Chapter Two' Trailer: The Losers' Club Returns to Derry, Maine |date=May 9, 2019 |first=Jordan |last=Moreau |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |access-date=May 23, 2019}}</ref>他還共同出演了[[約翰·克勞利|約翰·克勞利]]導演改編的{{link-en|唐娜·塔特|Donna Tartt}}小說《[[金翅雀|金翅雀]]》，扮演年輕的[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]學生和麻煩製造者鮑里斯·帕夫利科夫斯基（Boris Pavlikovsky）。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/stranger-things-star-finn-wolfhard-joins-ansel-elgort-goldfinch-1074809 |title='Stranger Things' Star Finn Wolfhard Joins Ansel Elgort in 'The Goldfinch' (Exclusive) |date=January 16, 2018 |first=Borys |last=Kit |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=January 16, 2018}}</ref>伍法德不是導演的首選。他曾想為鮑里斯選一個地道的[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]演員，但伍法德在試鏡時近乎完美的[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]口音幫助他得到了這個角色。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/goldfinch-trailer-breakdown-director-john-crowley/ |title=The Goldfinch: Trailer Breakdown With Director John Crowley |date=May 29, 2019 |first=John |last=Nugent |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=June 1, 2019}}</ref>同年，伍法德在10月11日首映的《[[阿達一族_(2019年電影)|阿達一族 (2019年電影)]]》動畫為 {{link-en|帕斯利·亞當斯|Pugsley Addams}}配音<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/06/charlize-theron-addams-family-cast-bette-midler-allison-janney-1202403723/|title='Addams Family' Movie Scares Up Charlize Theron, Bette Midler, Allison Janney & More For Voice Cast|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=June 5, 2018}}</ref>

2019年5月27日，伍法德在[[伊夫聖洛朗|伊夫聖洛朗]]的19秋冬系列廣告中首次亮相。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/stranger-things-finn-wolfhard-stars-in-the-latest-yves-saint-laurent-campaign|title=Stranger Things' Finn Wolfhard Stars In The Latest Yves Saint Laurent Campaign|work=[[Teen_Vogue|Teen Vogue]]|first=Kara|last=Nesvig|date=May 28, 2019|access-date=June 1, 2019}}</ref>

2020年1月，伍法德在[[安培林娛樂公司|安培林娛樂公司]]的超自然恐怖電影《{{link-en|豪門怨靈|The Turning}}》中扮演Miles，該電影改編自[[亨利·詹姆斯|亨利·詹姆斯]]的中篇小說{{link-en|碧廬冤孽|The Turn of the Screw}}<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/finn-wolfhard-horror-movie-turning-1202639379/ |title='Stranger Things' Actor Finn Wolfhard to Star in Haunted House Film 'The Turning' (EXCLUSIVE) |date=December 13, 2017 |first=Justin |last=Kroll |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |access-date=December 13, 2017}}</ref>，同時以[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]佈景的綜合電影首次亮相<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sundance.org/blogs/news/2020-sundance-features-announced|title=2020 SUNDANCE FILM FESTIVAL: 118 FEATURE FILMS ANNOUNCED|work=[[Sundance_Film_Festival|Sundance Film Festival]]|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=December 6, 2019}}</ref>, {{link-en|Omniboat: A Fast Boat Fantasia}},<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/2020-sundance-lineup-taylor-swift-viggo-mortensen-tessa-thompson/|title=Taylor Swift, Viggo Mortensen and Tessa Thompson Lead Diverse 2020 Sundance Lineup|work=[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]]|first=Beatrice|last=Verhoeven|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=December 6, 2019}}</ref>其中還包括[[勞勃·瑞福|勞勃·瑞福]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.deseret.com/utah/2019/12/4/20996264/sundance-film-festival-2020-robert-redford-taylor-swift-will-ferrell|title=Sundance 2020: Robert Redford will return to the big screen (Taylor Swift and Will Ferrell, too)|work=[[Deseret_News|Deseret News]]|first=Court|last=Mann|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=December 6, 2019}}</ref>由電影製作集體{{link-en|Borscht Corporation|Borscht Corp}}. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2019-12-04/sundance-2020-lineup-taylor-swift|title=Taylor Swift, Will Ferrell and Gloria Steinem lead an eclectic Sundance Film Festival 2020 lineup|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|first=Jen|last=Yamato|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=December 6, 2019}}</ref>伍法德然後製作了他的[[西南偏南|西南偏南]]（{{link-en|South by Southwest|SXSW}}）電影節於3月首次亮相，由{{link-en|傑里米·蕭林-里奧|Jeremy Schaulin-Rioux}}執導，Film Boldly製作了概念證明短片《Rules for Werewolves》，改編自劇作家和小說家柯克林恩的處女作劇本，將成為長篇電影，伍法德將在2020年底或2021年初擔任明星和製作。<ref name="DeadlineSXSW">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/stranger-things-finn-wolfhard-rules-for-werewolves-movie-1202870812/|title='Stranger Things' Finn Wolfhard To Star In 'Rules For Werewolves' Movie Based On SXSW Short|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=February 28, 2020|access-date=February 28, 2020}}</ref>他為兩部成人游泳作品配音：扎克·哈德爾和邁克爾·庫薩克的動畫特別版{{link-en|《微笑的朋友》|Smiling Friends}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.distractify.com/p/smiling-friends-cast|title='Smiling Friends' on Adult Swim Is Somehow Already a Hit Among Fans|website=distractify.com|first=Chrissy|last=Bobic|date=April 10, 2020|access-date=April 17, 2020}}</ref>，於 2020 年 4 月 1 日首播<ref>{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/nick-wolfhard-finn-wolfhard-smiling-friends-adult-swim/|title=Here's How Nick Wolfhard & Brother Finn Voiced Insane Creatures on 'Smiling Friends'|website=collider.com|first=Dave|last=Trumbore|date=April 16, 2020|access-date=April 17, 2020}}</ref> 和動畫系列{{link-en|JJ Villard's Fairy Tales}}作為Boypunzel一角，長髮公主的性別交換版本。伍法德加入了[[傑森·瑞特曼|傑森·瑞特曼]]執導的[[Quibi|Quibi]]電視劇改編{{link-en|家庭電影：公主新娘|Home Movie: The Princess Bride}}，為2020年7月上映的世界中央廚房籌集資金，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.looper.com/221665/quibi-just-announced-a-princess-bride-remake-you-never-expected-to-see/|title=Quibi just announced a Princess Bride remake you never expected to see|website=Looper.com|first=Nina|last=Starner|date=June 26, 2020|access-date=June 26, 2020}}</ref>然後現場閱讀{{link-en|家庭電影：公主新娘|Home Movie: The Princess Bride}}的劇本，作為孫子，2020年9月參加[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]]民主黨的慈善活動。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2020/09/princess-bride-wisconsin-democratic-party-1234573958/ | title = Whoopi Goldberg, Eric Idle Among Guests Added To 'Princess Bride' Reunion Script Reading | first=  Ted | last=  Johnson | date = September 9, 2020 | access-date = September 12, 2020 | work = [[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] }}</ref>

2020年8月，伍法德聯合主演了[[傑西·艾森柏格|傑西·艾森柏格]](Jesse Eisenberg) 編寫的有聲原創電影{{link-en|《當你完成拯救世界》|When You Finish Saving the World}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.playbill.com/article/jesse-eisenberg-to-be-joined-by-stranger-things-finn-wolfhard-in-new-audible-release|title=Jesse Eisenberg to be Joined by Stranger Things' Finn Wolfhard in New Audible Release|website=[[Playbill|Playbill]]|date=April 9, 2020|access-date=April 17, 2020}}</ref>個故事是從三個家庭成員的角度講述的，他們處於人生的不同階段。伍法德講述了Ziggy Katz，一個15歲的男孩，正在為未來的機器人治療師錄製音頻。<ref name="nytimes.com">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/02/books/jesse-eisenberg-when-you-finish-saving-the-world-audio.html|title=It's a Book. It's a Podcast. It's a Three-Act Play, in Your Ears.|website=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=August 2, 2020|access-date=August 8, 2020}}</ref>此外，有聲讀物將被改編成喜劇電影，[[A24_(公司)|A24 (公司)]]的{{link-en|《當你完成拯救世界》|When You Finish Saving the World }}由[[茱莉安·摩爾|茱莉安·摩爾]]和伍法德將演出母子，[[傑西·艾森柏格|傑西·艾森柏格]]執導和編劇，[[茱莉安·摩爾|茱莉安·摩爾]]製作,[[艾瑪·史東|艾瑪·史東]]和{{link-en|戴夫・麥卡瑞|Dave McCary}}生產。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/julianne-moore-finn-wolfhard-star-jesse-eisenberg-comedy-when-you-finish-saving-world-with-emma-stone-producing-1202903425/|title=Hot Project Du Jour: Julianne Moore & Finn Wolfhard To Star In Jesse Eisenberg-Directed 'When You Finish Saving The World' Based On Audible Original; Emma Stone Producing|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=April 9, 2020|access-date=April 17, 2020}}</ref>2020年7月15日，宣布伍法德和他的哥哥Nick Wolfhard將成為科幻動畫系列NEW-GEN的配音演員，與[[安雅·夏隆查|安雅·夏隆查]]一起扮演雙胞胎兄弟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/stranger-things-finn-wolfhard-new-gen-sci-fi-1234705934/|title='Stranger Things' Star Finn Wolfhard, 'Witcher's' Anya Chalotra Set For Sci-Fi Animation 'New-Gen' (EXCLUSIVE)|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Naman|last=Ramachandran|date=July 15, 2020|access-date=July 15, 2020}}</ref>此外，2020年8月19日，宣布伍法德已加入導演[[吉勒摩·戴托羅|吉勒摩·戴托羅]]的定格動畫音樂長片《[[木偶奇遇記_(2021年電影)|木偶奇遇記]]，替小燈芯配音。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/guillermo-del-toro-signs-netflix-deal-casts-tilda-swinton-finn-wolfhard-in-pinocchio-exclusive|title=Guillermo del Toro Casts Tilda Swinton, Finn Wolfhard in 'Pinocchio,' Signs Netflix Deal (Exclusive)|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=August 19, 2020|access-date=August 20, 2020}}</ref>

