===音樂===
除了表演之外，伍法德還是[[溫哥華|溫哥華]][[加拿大|加拿大]][[另類搖滾|另類搖滾]]樂團[[Calpurnia樂團|Calpurnia樂團]]的主唱、吉他手和詞曲作者，樂團直到於2019年11月正式解散。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/stranger-things-star-finn-wolfhands-band-calpurnia-have-split-up-2574329#BUC3ZAE2I7ohYL0x.99 |title='Stranger Things' star Finn Wolfhard's band Calpurnia have split up |last=Jones |first=Damian |date=November 8, 2019 |work=NME |access-date=December 1, 2019}}</ref>他們曾與[[美國|美國]]&[[加拿大|加拿大]]的{{link-en|皇家山唱片公司|Royal Mountain Records}}簽約以及[[歐洲|歐洲]]和[[英國|英國]]的{{link-en|Transgressive Records}}、paradYse。

幾週後，宣布伍法德與[[Calpurnia樂團|Calpurnia樂團]]鼓手Malcolm Craig的組了新的樂團[[The_Aubreys樂團|The Aubreys樂團]]將在他的電影《{{link-en|豪門怨靈|The Turning}}》的配樂中首次亮相。<ref name="Jones">{{cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/stranger-things-star-finn-wolfhard-is-back-with-a-new-band-2576822 |title='Stranger Things' star Finn Wolfhard is back with a new band |last=Jones |first=Damian |date=November 21, 2019 |work=NME |access-date=December 1, 2019}}</ref>[[The_Aubreys樂團|The Aubreys樂團]]於2020年3月10日發行了他們的單曲“Loved One”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/rock/9330803/the-aubreys-loved-one-finn-wolfhard |title=Finn Wolfhard's New Band The Aubreys Unveil Jangling 'Loved One': Exclusive |last=Rowley |first=Glenn |date=March 10, 2020 |work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]] |access-date=April 17, 2020}}</ref>和他們的首張EP“Soda & Pie”由{{link-en|AWAL|AWAL}}唱片公司於2020年3月13日發行。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/finn-wolfhard-the-aubreys-interview-soda-and-pie-ep-calpurnia-split-beastie-boys-2624983|title=Finn Wolfhard on new band The Aubreys: “We wanted to mix the craziness of Flaming Lips with the earnestness of Wilco”}}</ref>他們的下一首單曲“Smoke Bomb”於2020年8月17日發行。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.altpress.com/features/aubreys-smoke-bomb-single-finn-wolfhard-interview/|title=Here’s how Joe Keery helped Finn Wolfhard on the Aubreys’ new single}}</ref>《No Offerings》是The Aubreys樂團與Lunar Vacation第一張合作的單曲，於2021年1月12日發行。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.altpress.com/features/finn-wolfhard-the-aubreys-lunar-vacation-no-offerings/|title=Here’s how the Aubreys’Finn Wolfhard crafted their first collab}}</ref>2021年的第二張單曲《Sand in My Bed》在2月14日。《Karaoke Alone》專輯於2021年11月5日發行 ,是他們第一張LP專輯（[[黑膠唱片|黑膠唱片]]）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-aubreys-announce-debut-album-karaoke-alone-share-title-track-3042804|title=The Aubreys announce their debut album ‘Karaoke Alone’ and share title track}}</ref>

